DAT
id=qid::label=str::text=lstr::
5562::$$$message_0050_0000_0000$$$::Soon after Fuji-nee leaves, I lock up and Sakura and I leave as well.::
5563::$$$message_0050_0001_0000$$$::"..."[lr]::
5564::$$$message_0050_0001_0001$$$::"Sakura? What's wrong? You don't look good. Are you still feeling sick?"::
5565::$$$message_0050_0002_0000$$$::"Eh? Oh, no. I'm feeling better. What about you? You didn't look well this morning, and the injury you had from yesterday might have gotten worse."[lr]::
5566::$$$message_0050_0002_0001$$$::Yesterday's injury?[lr]::
5567::$$$message_0050_0002_0002$$$::Oh, the bruise on my left hand.::
5568::$$$message_0050_0003_0000$$$::"Well, the bruise hasn't changed much. My hand just swelled up, so it should get better soon."[lr]::
5569::$$$message_0050_0003_0001$$$::"..."[lr]::
5570::$$$message_0050_0003_0002$$$::Sakura continues to stare at me, looking concerned.::
5571::$$$message_0050_0004_0000$$$::"Uh, I'm fine. Really. It's nothing."[lr]::
5572::$$$message_0050_0004_0001$$$::"..."[lr]::
5573::$$$message_0050_0004_0002$$$::"What's going on? You've been acting weird since yesterday, Sakura. This is just a bruise. Or what... Is this your way of admitting it happened because you came in the middle of the night and stomped on my hand while I was sleeping?"::
5574::$$$message_0050_0005_0000$$$::"S-Senpai! I'm not that heavy! I was just...well..."[lr]::
5575::$$$message_0050_0005_0001$$$::"Just, what?"[lr]::
5576::$$$message_0050_0005_0002$$$::"...I just hope it's just my mistake..."::
5577::$$$message_0050_0006_0000$$$::"Huh?"[lr]::
5578::$$$message_0050_0006_0001$$$::I don't get what Sakura's saying.[lr]::
5579::$$$message_0050_0006_0002$$$::Sakura may be quiet, but she generally speaks her mind.[lr]::
5580::$$$message_0050_0006_0003$$$::It's not like her to beat around the bush so much.::
5581::$$$message_0050_0007_0000$$$::"Senpai. I would like to ask you a favor."[lr]::
5582::$$$message_0050_0007_0001$$$::"Sure, as long as it's within something I can do. What's up?" [lr]::
5583::$$$message_0050_0007_0002$$$::"Well, I can't come help you tonight and tomorrow. So...at least for then, will you try to stay in your home as much as possible?"::
5584::$$$message_0050_0008_0000$$$::"Huh? Are you saying I need to skip work on Sunday, too?"[lr]::
5585::$$$message_0050_0008_0001$$$::"Yes. I would like you to stay in your house as much as you can. Um, I'll come back and help once I'm done with my errand."::
5586::$$$message_0050_0009_0000$$$::"Hmmm. Well, I guess skipping one day of work wouldn't hurt.[lr]::
5587::$$$message_0050_0009_0001$$$::Okay. I'll just hang around the house all day over the weekend. Is that what you want, Sakura?"[lr]::
5588::$$$message_0050_0009_0002$$$::"Yes. That would be a really big help."::
5589::$$$message_0050_0010_0000$$$::A bit of relaxation actually doesn't sound so bad.[lr]::
5590::$$$message_0050_0010_0001$$$::I've been working nonstop recently, so I have some extra funds right now. Maybe I'll clean out all the junk this weekend.:ّ=